Lots of love, and I'll see you in a video very soon :) - Michael

#prsguitars #guitargate

@chinaguitarsceptic - Man, I'll never forget how kind you were to me and how much we laughed in the short time we got to hang out. I sincerely wish we could've done it just one more time. We travel so far in our one life, and some people we meet just make a permanent dent. Mike did that. He smiled constantly. He lifted people up. He was endlessly encouraging and really funny in a way Americans simply cannot be. He was also so humble and hopeful and gracious. Even in his last video, where he had AI speak in his voice, he expressed a hope and a blessing for all of us. Like Mike used to say - "Take good Care." Love you brother. Rest easy my friend.

HUGE CONGRATS TO JMAC who won the @prsguitars guitar / amp / accessories rig in our recent giveaway! Also - another subscriber donated a full pedalboard to JMAC! Endlessly grateful for this community we've built together. Enjoy it brother!! #prs #prsguitars #guitarlessons
